<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no" ?>
<FinalDraft DocumentType="Script" Template="No" Version="4">

  <Content>
    <Paragraph Type="New Act">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Prime" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="Underline">ACT ONE</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="1" Page="1" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="ALAN">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="EMILY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="JULIET">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT. ALAN’S HOUSE - DAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>In a fast DADDY MONTAGE we see ALAN being a lovable super dad to his girls EMILY (5) and JULIET (3). MUSIC: An annoying kid’s song but covered by a band that was cool in 2001. Think </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Prime" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Cocomelon’s</Text>
      <Text> MY DADDY IS THE BEST performed by Blink 182.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>- Alan and the girls paint on big easels.
- Alan, wearing a pirate hat, chases the girls who scream with joy. Juliet somehow gets a real knife and a terrified Alan tries to take it from her.
- Alan reads the girls a children’s biography of Ruth Bader-Ginsburg.
- Alan puts an icepack on a crying Juliet and hugs her.
- Alan pretends to fight a stuffed animal snake. The snake wins and Alan dies, then pops back up as a silly zombie. It’s a very physical bit and the girls cackle with glee.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Alan, tired but proud of what a great dad he is, stops for a La Croix break.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>EMILY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Do it again!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>ALAN</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Daddy needs a break.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>JULIET</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Please!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>ALAN</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Come on, it’s time for lunch. It’s already--</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Alan checks his phone: </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Prime" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="Bold">9:13 AM</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>ALAN</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Nine thirteen!? NINE-THIRTEEN!?!? How could it possibly be nine-fucking-thirteen? We did like ten things! I inflated </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Prime" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="Underline">and deflated</Text>
      <Text> a bouncy castle! </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Prime" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Aaaaggh</Text>
      <Text>!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>The girls stare at him, unmoved.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>EMILY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Let’s put glitter on the cat.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>JULIET</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I have some.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Center" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
  </Content>

